/*
********************************************

	Macro Title: toggle hex color
	Description:
	This macro is specific to the PF2E Kingmaker module. It will toggle the "Show Colored Hexes" option.

 Foundry Version: 12
 Last updated 12-Nov-2024

 Use case: I personally use this macro to toggle hex colors that show status (reconniotered, mapped, etc) 
 on a user that has the UI hidden because I am using it to record or stream andf the tool is not available.
 
********************************************
*/

game.coloredAndIconsLayer.visible=!game.coloredAndIconsLayer.visible;game.coloredAndIconsLayer.draw()
